Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Pirate Era is experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:37.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a groundswell beyond the World \NGovernment's expectation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being at the center of the unstoppable swell\Nand drawing the most attention is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to cope with the \Nturbulent Great Pirate Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50 leaders hold the World Conference\Nevery four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the Reverie, it is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The times are changing drastically now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Marco!\NThe Keeper of Whitebeard's Last Memento!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that I've \Nwanted since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:49.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place looks terrible, too.\NThere are traces of robberies across the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MINK TRIBE GUARDIANS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Cat Viper's navigation \Nskill was quite formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd expected from a man\Nwho sailed on the ship of the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how much longer should we wait\Nin these ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Master Cat Viper brings Marco here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll show...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Marco comes along with us to the Land of Wano,\Nhe'll make for a strong ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco is the former 1st division commander of\Nthe infamous Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call him Marco the Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to know \Nthat he's Master's friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go take a look at that man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master told you to wait here\Nbecause you-{\i1}gara{\i0} got a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Is he the kind of guy\Nwho'll get frightened by my face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said there is a peaceful village\Non the other side of a cave at the back of that waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A group of warriors like us\Nwill scare its residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Master Cat Viper's \Nface is scarier than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, when he gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But he's cute when he smiles.\N--Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His treatment is finished.\NHe can go now-{\i1}yoi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you can go now.\NTama, can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flames of Restoration only \Nhave a limited effect on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:22.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MARCO\NFORMER 1ST DIVISION COMMANDER (SHIP'S DOCTOR)\NOF THE WHITEBEARD PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been treated and I know \Nit'll be restored faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be jumping around by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Marco's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're okay now, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "By tomorrow."\NDon't jump yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The 1st division commander of the \NWhitebeard Pirates, Marco the Phoenix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:14.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's Whitebeard's right-hand man\Nwho fought at the front lines...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in the Paramount War\Nagainst the Navy two years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even rarer than Logia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Zoan Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the 1st division commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of attack he absorbs,\Nhe recovers by flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco the Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:08:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The members of the Whitebeard Pirates\Ncalled their leader, Whitebeard, "pops"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Whitebeard called them his "sons."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They had incomparable cohesion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?!\NAnswer me, Squard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Squard once had all of his pirate \Ncrew killed by Gold Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Navy Admiral Akainu artfully manipulated\Nhis deep grudge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He told him the truth\Nthat Ace was actually Roger's son{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and lied that Whitebeard sold\Nthe Whitebeard Pirates' lives to the Navy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in exchange for Ace's life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, son, even if you are a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how much you hate Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so much so that I can feel your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Squard, it's ridiculous to lay the blame on a child\Nfor the sins of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ace do something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn who Ace's father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all met each other on \Nthis wide sea by chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only the two of you\Nbut all of you, I take as my sons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Squard, treat him kindly.\NI don't love him any more than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all family to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, back Straw Hat Luffy up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Whitebeard Pirates' support,\NLuffy successfully freed Ace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Whitebeard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give you an order from the Captain\None last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you and I will split up from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, survive at any cost\Nand go back to the New World safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a remnant from the old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no ship that can bear me\Nin the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, you guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me one thing, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!\NI'm glad that I'm present at your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one that I \Nrefuse to call my son, Teech!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke the one and \Nonly iron rule on my ship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you killed your mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge the 4th division \Ncommander - Thatch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by taking this fool's life \Nthereby ending the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I'm out of bullets!\NHey, give me another gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man that Roger is waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is not you, Teech, at any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me, my sons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I raised such a ridiculous fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys gave me everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been traveling a very long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd! What kind of pirate\Ndoesn't have interest in treasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Newgate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that I've \Nwanted since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have something?\NWhy don't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A family?"\NWhat is he talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have deep appreciation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye, my sons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whitebeard died!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The feud with Blackbeard\Nseemed to have ended by Whitebeard's death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, his true motive \Nwas revealed thereafter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put on a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a show that will shake the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Dark-Dark Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pose is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity of darkness brings\Ntotal annihilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the power of tremor\Ndestroys everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I possess them both!\NNo one can compete with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the strongest man in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Teech who ripped off the power\Nfrom Whitebeard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would later be known to the world\Nas one of the Four Emperors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,--Marco...\N--Marco-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:54.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...I got bad stiff shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CAT VIPER - MINK TRIBE GUARDIANS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco, at the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco, the vegetables in my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco, my back hurts again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Marco-{\i1}chan{\i0}, my knees...\N--Marco, help me study...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco, my little brother is mean to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right-{\i1}yoi{\i0}.\NI'm gonna listen to you all in order-{\i1}yoi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the village Pops built-{\i1}yoi{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The good old man Whitebeard?\NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of their extreme poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can't pay their Heavenly Tribute\Nand affiliate themselves with the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it goes with\Nthe non-affiliated countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates and kidnappers do as they like\Nand those islands become lawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The countries go to ruin\Nand tons of children become orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops was one of those children-yoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He set out to sea at an early age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he became a pirate,\Nhe cared about this island
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and continued sending dirty money and resources\Nwithout revealing his identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he didn't have a family from the start\Nand all his friends were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this corrupt world,\Nthere's no such a thing as clean money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you-{\i1}yoi{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Paramount War,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we at least tried to defend\Nthe things that Pops was protecting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we started the Grudge War against Blackbeard\Nwho came to invade our territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were no match for Teech\Nsince he even got Pops' fruit-power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took everything away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to beat the hell \Nout of that ingrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was actually stingy, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He often wanted other people's drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never bought us drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he was passing\Nall of his share of treasure to this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this village is the last memento\Nthat he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Red-Haired buried him nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Warlord named Weevil\Nis proclaiming he's Pops' biological son
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacking people connected to Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard's son, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beard's white as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only biological son of\Nthe world's strongest pirate, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman who Whitebeard loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a man-loves-woman thing\Nso I don't know for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess they're after his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't take our word for \Nit that there isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both this place and I will become their target\Nsooner or later-{\i1}yoi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can't leave-{\i1}meow{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weevil's mother Buckin used to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know 30-something years or nearly 40 years ago,\Nshe was on the same ship with Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe he's also a memento\Nthat should be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His behavior tells me otherwise-{\i1}yoi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to see Straw Hat Luffy,\NI want you to pass on a message, Cat Viper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You said you're gonna go to the Land of Wano?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Emperor of the Sea - Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, that fool...\NIs he gonna pick a fight with Kaido this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:05.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Straw Hats enter an unknown sea area!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:09.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they be able to reach the Land of \NWano that is shut to all outsiders?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Climbing Up a Waterfall!\NA Great Journey Through the Land of Wano's Sea Zone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick the Emperor \Nof the Sea, Kaido's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tough enemies are waiting for him!\NSamurai, shogun, and ninja!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One Piece! The Land of Wano \NArc will finally begin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:36.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LAND OF WANO ARC STARTS \NSUNDAY, JULY 7TH! (JST)
